.
</emphasis>
Sternite VII (
<figureCitation id="644AA0EAF769EDE744FD448AF2294568" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Fig. 20</figureCitation>
) in ventral view with posterior margin concave, lateral margins convex and surface with setae. Pygofer (
<figureCitation id="EAE914F5F94C42DF3DCB30C987AFC6A7" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Figs 18</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="C2B79F03F2DBA849B7FDEAB1C689A7D5" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">19</figureCitation>
) in lateral view irregularly quadrilateral, with setae; in ventral view oblong, base slightly acute. Anal tube (
<figureCitation id="5356666F846E04809AC459C8F4AB2909" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Figs 18</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="CABADB739F4538F3C4810AC60A164D29" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">19</figureCitation>
) small and oval. Valvifer I (
<figureCitation id="2E74A3B5EF67F2AE2100A1117C4A29B1" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Fig. 21</figureCitation>
) semicircular and thin; valvulae I knife-shaped, apical three-fourths of dorsal surface sculptured, ventral surface of the apex with a row of small toothed processes. Valvifer II (
<figureCitation id="5240DBD100054D93F4CF972B29A087E5" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Fig. 23</figureCitation>
) shoe-shaped in lateral view, dorsal margin membranous. Basal part of valvulae II (
<figureCitation id="3B4A69A669E687C1CC9EE03E76023D43" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Fig. 22</figureCitation>
) connected to the apex of 
<normalizedToken id="43C448EA8B8A8D9E85802A7BEEB2E3A1" originalValue="“sole”">&quot;sole&quot;</normalizedToken>
, ramus slender, parallel-sided and evenly curved in basal two-thirds, apex slightly broadened with two indistinct and widely spaced dorsal preapical tooth processes; the one-third of apical broaden slightly. Gonoplac (
<figureCitation id="F2B9AA2375D704F8DDA72FE86F4B68DB" captionStart="Figures 18–23" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 18 - 23. Sinocentrus brevicornis Li &amp; Chen, sp. nov. 18 female genitalia, lateral view 19 female genitalia, ventral view 20 sternite VII, ventral view 21 valvifer I and valvulae I, lateral view 22 valvulae II, lateral view 23 valvifer II and gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/352860" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" tableDoi="10.3897/zookeys.886.36672.figures18-23">Fig. 23</figureCitation>
) connected to base of 
<normalizedToken id="A1194E700E89FA1ADE5A325FB68C6177" originalValue="“sole”">&quot;sole&quot;</normalizedToken>
, apical third expanded, ventral margin with setae.
</paragraph>
